d racing and spurred an investigation into the causes.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky_Derby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4197966363369034e-21, \"text\": \"Kentucky Derby\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky_Derby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky_Derby\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Churchill_Downs\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5118116658500695e-20, \"text\": \"Churchill Downs\", \"types\": [\"Q1777138\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Churchill_Downs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Churchill_Downs\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Horse racing\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"similar reckonings\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"most prominently a spate\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"deaths\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"the causes\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while the implementation of HISA and other reforms have succeeded at reducing fatalities, this is another reminder of how controversial incidents threaten the existence of animal sports in the 21st century.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the implementation\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"HISA\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2260}, {\"ngram\": \"other reforms\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"fatalities\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"another reminder\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"how controversial incidents\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"the existence\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"animal sports\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"the 21st century\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are all living in a different time when it comes to equine sports, and I think because of that we all have to be a lot more careful,\\\" thoroughbred trainer Graham Motion told the AP in a phone interview.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\", \"score\": 0.9999999996584847, \"rank\": 3.13107143439196e-10, \"text\": \"Graham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q188094\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1281808445271634e-14, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different time\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"equine sports\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"a phone interview\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of us are all about the welfare of the animals, but we can not take it for granted.\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"the welfare\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"the animals\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have to show that that's what we are about.\\\"\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lazarus, who worked for FEI for six years from 2009-15 as general counsel and then chief of business strategy and development, said folks in horse racing have learned it is not enough just to say they love horses and care about them.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lazarus_of_Bethany\", \"score\": 0.9999919062547761, \"rank\": 8.0938106675477e-06, \"text\": \"Lazarus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lazarus_of_Bethany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lazarus_of_Bethany\"}, {\"begin\": 2806, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4920359798164935e-48, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six years\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"general counsel\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"business strategy\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"development\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"folks\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2919}, {\"ngram\": \"horse racing\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being really transparent about everything that you are doing is important,\\\" Lazarus said.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3094, \"end\": 3101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lazarus_of_Bethany\", \"score\": 0.9999919062547761, \"rank\": 8.0938106675477e-06, \"text\": \"Lazarus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lazarus_of_Bethany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lazarus_of_Bethany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain equestrian rider Carl Hester, who said he was shocked by the video of 